{"id":10000004,"title":".gitignore不生效问题解决方法","introduction":"探寻.gitignore为神马不生效的，怎么去解决这个问题","cover":"https://joyimg.lexujia.com/blog/article-cover/202604/316cd35c-2c78-43d9-87fc-3b6b7b368f0f.png","classifyId":100001,"columnId":100005,"userId":10009,"content":"<h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">1. 检查<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code>.gitignore</code></span>文件的位置和语法</h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">确保你的</span>.gitignore<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">文件放在正确的位置</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">2. 确认<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code>.gitignore</code></span>文件的生效</h3><pre><code class=\"language-css\">git rm -r --cached .\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \".gitignore is now working\"\n</code></pre><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">3. 检查文件状态</h3><pre><code >git status</code></pre><p>4. 清除缓存</p><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">4. 清除缓存</h3><pre><code >git rm -r --cached .\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"Update ignored files\"</code></pre><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">5. 使用<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code>git check-ignore</code></span>命令</h3><pre><code >git check-ignore -v 文件路径</code></pre><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">6. 确保<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code>.gitignore</code></span>文件没有被错误地修改或覆盖</h3><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">7. 重新克隆仓库</h3><pre><code >git clone [repository-url] [new-directory]\n</code></pre><p><br></p>","readType":1,"isStick":2,"state":1,"isOriginal":2,"reprintAddress":null,"isRecommend":2,"readership":0,"keywords":".gitignore","userSource":2,"createTime":"2026-02-25 23:05:26","updateTime":"2026-05-20 17:18:59","likeCount":0,"classifyName":"运维部署","labels":[100011],"labelNames":["git"],"userName":"徐徐乐之","userAvatar":"http://localhost:8000/article/08eee589-49e0-437c-987wdq.png","columnName":"前端哪些事"}